  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网边缘节点设计一个事件驱动的处理流程。核心思路是：当聚合根产生事件后，先持久化到事件存储，然后通过反应器推送到队列，最后由队列工作器执行具体的副作用操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我理解整体链路是 Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect。想确认一下：Reactor 和 Queue Worker 是两个独立的参与者吗？还是可以把它们合并？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue Worker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是两个独立的角色。Reactor 负责监听事件并推送任务到队列，它本身不执行业务逻辑；Queue Worker 才是真正拉取任务并执行副作用的组件。这样解耦可以支持水平扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把六个参与者按顺序排列好了。现在标注消息流：Aggregate 向 Event Store 发送 Store Event，Event Store 向 Reactor 发送 Dispatch Event，Reactor 向 Queue 推送任务，Queue 把工作分配给 Worker，最后 Worker 执行 Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加上异常处理的分支。当 Side Effect 执行后，如果成功，Worker 要标记任务已完成；如果失败，需要支持重试机制。这个用 alt 片段来表达比较合适。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加 alt 分支：Success 路径是 Side Effect 返回成功，Worker 标记任务完成；Failure 路径是返回失败，Worker 触发重试。两个分支都回到 Queue 的状态变更。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Retry Job",
        "Mark Job as Completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "重试的逻辑需要再明确一下——是 Worker 直接重试，还是把任务重新推回队列？从图上看 W-Q: Retry Job 像是状态更新，但实际应该是重新进入队列等待调度吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我调整一下表达。Retry Job 表示 Worker 通知 Queue 更新任务状态为待重试，Queue 后续会重新调度给 Worker。这样符合消息驱动的语义，而不是 Worker 直接循环调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样逻辑就通顺了。整个流程覆盖了事件存储、异步分发、队列缓冲、副作用执行以及失败重试，完整呈现了 IoT 工业边缘节点的事件驱动架构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
